      "updated": 1773380121492,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "9. When Should We Use Flows?\n\nUse flows when:\n\nBuilding multi-step AI applications\n\nCreating automation pipelines\n\nWorking with multiple agents\n\nManaging complex workflows\n\nExamples:\n\nAI research assistant\n\nAI content generator\n\nCustomer support automation\n\nData processing pipelines",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "9. When Should We Use Flows?\n\nUse flows when:\n\nBuilding multi-step AI applications\n\nCreating automation pipelines\n\nWorking with multiple agents\n\nManaging complex workflows\n\nExamples:\n\nAI research assistant\n\nAI content generator\n\nCustomer support automation\n\nData processing pipelines",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
