      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "11. Key Takeaway\n\nCrewAI Flows allow you to build:\n\nStep-by-step AI workflows\n\nEvent-driven pipelines\n\nScalable AI automation\n\nMain decorators:\n\n@start  → Start the flow\n@listen → Trigger next step",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "11. Key Takeaway\n\nCrewAI Flows allow you to build:\n\nStep-by-step AI workflows\n\nEvent-driven pipelines\n\nScalable AI automation\n\nMain decorators:\n\n@start  → Start the flow\n@listen → Trigger next step",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
